* Developed by Spiros Bond
* Created April 2017

This program will enable your Raspberry Pi to read the values from a 2 accelerometers using the I2C interface of a Raspberry PI.
It also stores all measurements in a csv.

Go here for more information;

http://ozzmaker.com/berryimu/

Compile with;
make all

To run;
./pi_2accel_berryIMU.o "filename"



